HEADWORD: Miliaria
<hw>Mil`i*a"ri*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Miliary</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A fever accompanied by
an eruption of small, isolated, red pimples, resembling a millet seed in
form or size; miliary fever.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

